SOME POSSIBLE OPTIONS involving AngularJS:

(1)The HTML files contain ng-Show directives to reveal all the concealed files.

The concealed files will only be revealed based on choice of buttons (What is your name?/How old are you?/Are you married?/etc).

https://www.w3schools.com/angular/angular_htmldom.asp
--------------> https://www.w3schools.com/angular/tryit.asp?filename=try_ng_html_show


....or.....


